      "instruction": "<p>Boil a full kettle</p><p>Heat a large dry pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> flaked almonds</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until toasted and lightly golden, reserve the pan</p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk to make sure they don't burn!</p>",
