    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> spinach</strong> to a colander and pour <strong>boiled water</strong> all over it so that it starts to wilt</p><p>Rinse the <strong>wilted spinach</strong> under the <strong>cold running water</strong> until it's cool</p><p>Once cool, squeeze the water out of the spinach as much as you can then chop it roughly</p><p>Reboil a full kettle </p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
