    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel the<strong> garlic</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>wilted spinach </strong>and most of the<strong> basil </strong>(reserve a few leaves for garnish) to a <strong>food processor </strong>with the <strong>toasted almonds</strong>, <strong>peeled garlic</strong> and <strong>half</strong> the <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong></p><p>Add the juice of 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span> <strong>lemon</strong>, 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil </strong>and 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp] </span><strong>cold water </strong>with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong>,<strong> </strong>then blitz until well combined and smooth – this is your <strong>spinach & basil pesto</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
