    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium-high heat with a little drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>diced chorizo</strong> and cook for 5-6 min or until golden and crispy</p><p>Meanwhile, peel and finely chop the<strong> shallot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Dissolve the <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> in 500ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[850ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
