    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut the <strong>remaining lemon</strong> into wedges</p><p>Serve the <strong>chorizo & pesto orzo</strong> in bowls topped with the <strong>panko-crusted heritage beef tomato</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining basil leaves </strong>and a <strong>lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
